    <h2>Pre-School Learning Resource Center</h2>
    <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/665420ea445064a3ad56323a/665420ea445064a3ad563352_Preschool.png" class="w3-circle" alt="Alps">
        <br>The Pre-School Learning Resource Center provides young learners with a welcoming space for
        reading, exploration, and discovery. The collection comprises of picture books, board books,
        classic and award-winning titles, books about community helpers, social-emotional learning,
        science and nature. Additionally, the library provides manipulative resources that allow children
        to engage in exploratory play, learn through experimentation, and develop problem-solving
        skills.
        Spaces for play and physical exercise are also provided wherein sportsmanship among children
        is being develop.
        *Opens from Monday to Friday, 7:00 AM to 3:00 PM; Saturdays, 8:00 AM to 12:00 NN.</p>

